sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/UI
    participant Hub as Hub
    participant Queue as Task Queue
    participant Worker as Worker

    User->>Hub: Submit goal
    Hub->>Hub: Validate policy, defaults, team scope
    Hub->>Hub: Create goal + trace_id + plan
    Hub->>Queue: Materialize delegated tasks
    Hub->>Worker: Delegate executable task
    Worker-->>Hub: Result + verification evidence
    Hub->>Hub: Verification + governance summary
    Hub-->>User: Artifact-first result with drilldown
